                "caption": "Figure 1:Overview of Entrocraft. It uses entropy-guided rejection sampling to filter rollouts against a target entropy, enabling precise control over the entropy curve throughout RL training. This control addresses performance saturation, a key obstacle to scaling RL. We find that a linear annealing schedule performs best, improving generalization, output diversity, and sustained training.",
